::KitKat::

She ran through the ship making sure everyone had escaped.  She ran 
back to Phobia,"Come on and let's get going.  I don't want to lose 
any more bots today."

She ran towards an escape hatch. She opened her link, "You can't save 
it Phobia, let's go."  She wanted to stay to make sure Phobia made it 
out safely, but she still had her other team mates to think about.
 She entered into the hatch and looked back one last time, "COME ON 
PHOBIA! Let's get out now!"

She closed her eyes and jumped out of the hatch.

She fell to earth.  If felt like an eternity before she hit the 
trees.  She went craching down, through branches and leaves and 
needles.  She hit the ground with a thud.  She lay there for a moment 
and looked up into the sky, "Come on Phobia, come on.  Don't stay to 
die, come on please."

She lowered her head and lay on the ground, wondering how many ribs 
she broke on the way down.
